summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lot 22, Block 68, Lake Union Shore Lands Addition, and the north 42 feet of Lot 2, Block 20, Dewey's Addition; with respect to Use, Height and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto three new sections numbered 2-259, 10-16 and 17-206, respectively.
